# Setlist Ultra mobile

Read `docs/BUILD.md` and `apps/mobile/AGENTS.md` before editing Metro, Babel, Gradle, or release scripts.

## Must keep

- `metro.config.js`: `extraNodeModules` for `@setlist-ultra/*`, `wasm` in `assetExts`, `blockList` for `android/build`
- `babel.config.js`: `react-native-reanimated/plugin` as last plugin
- Release APKs only for users (`assembleRelease`); debug APKs need Metro on the dev machine
- Run `npm run preflight` before `expo start` or `android:apk`

## Must not

- Ship debug APKs to GitHub Releases
- Run `gradlew clean` on Windows with `S:` subst paths
- Remove expo-router junction/symlink setup without fixing root resolution
- Commit `releases/*.apk` (CI publishes to GitHub Releases)

## Release checklist

1. `npm run preflight && npm run typecheck`
2. `git tag vX.Y.Z && git push origin vX.Y.Z`
3. Wait for CI; verify APK with embedded bundle
4. Smoke test on device: app opens, demo song visible
